  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Product Design Lead (Home Fragrance / Consumer Products)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Company Description</strong></h2><p>Our client is a premium fragrance and lifestyle brand expanding globally across home fragrance, hotel scenting systems, and consumer lifestyle products. The brand emphasises refined aesthetics, natural materials, and structured design language, and is strengthening its in-house product development capability. </p><h2><strong>Job Description</strong></h2><p>The Product Design Lead will be responsible for leading product design direction and development for consumer fragrance products. This role combines design leadership, product understanding, and collaboration with production and fragrance teams to ensure commercially viable and brand-aligned products.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Lead the concept development of new product series</p></li><li><p>Define and maintain a consistent premium design language</p></li><li><p>Work on product packaging, material selection, and structural design</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with fragrance development and production teams to ensure product feasibility</p></li><li><p>Apply understanding of materials, performance, and product functionality in design decisions</p></li><li><p>Guide and coordinate design execution across internal or remote design teams</p></li><li><p>Support the development of structured product design systems and workflows</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Relevant experience in product design or product development within consumer or lifestyle products</p></li><li><p>Strong aesthetic sense aligned with premium product positioning</p></li><li><p>Understanding of materials, structural design, and production feasibility</p></li><li><p>Ability to work cross-functionally with technical and production stakeholders</p></li><li><p>Portfolio demonstrating product design work is required</p></li></ul><p><strong>EA License No:</strong> 23C1703<br /><strong>EA Personnel No:</strong> R1762582<br /><strong>EA Personnel Name:</strong> Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p>",
